# Preset 08: Protocol — multi-turn with tools
# Simulates a full agent turn: thought → action → result → response

<stream>
<thought>Let me list the directory first.</thought>
<action type="tool" name="list" id="ls1" mode="sync">{"path":"src/"}</action>
<result id="ls1" status="ok">{"count":5,"results":"agent.cpp\nagent.hpp\nmain.cpp\nMakefile\nconfig/"}</result>
<thought>Good, I see the source files. Let me search for TODOs.</thought>
<action type="tool" name="grep" id="g1" mode="sync">{"pattern":"TODO","path":"src/"}</action>
<result id="g1" status="ok">{"matches":["src/core/agent.cpp:45:TODO: add retry logic","src/main.cpp:12:TODO: parse config"]}</result>

<response final="true">
Found **2 TODOs**:

- `src/core/agent.cpp:45` — add retry logic
- `src/main.cpp:12` — parse config
</response>
</stream>

---EXPECT---
# Actions appear with icons
renders_action: list
renders_action: grep
# Results shown
contains: agent.cpp
contains: TODO: add retry logic
contains: TODO: parse config
# Final response has markdown rendering
contains: 2 TODOs
contains: bold rendering for "**2 TODOs**"
# Order is preserved
order: [thought, action_list, result_list, thought, action_grep, result_grep, response]
